                "typeId": 1,
                "questionText": "Cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/6e91f04f-d083-4d7e-ab45-bbcf8008efdb.png\"/> vuông tại <i>A</i> có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c8f0f87a-fca0-435a-97c5-9e32be9ffcf1.png\"/> Kẻ đường cao <i>AH</i> <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/96228559-0852-4ee2-ba58-afe3d1085a6f.png\"/>\n<br>a) Chứng minh: \n<br>b) Vẽ <i>BE</i> là phân giác của góc <i>ABC, F</i> là giao điểm của<i> AH</i> và <i>BE</i>. Chứng minh: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/0e872bf1-24ec-4ab1-895f-b5049c459458.png\"/>\n<br>c) Tính độ dài <i>AF</i>.\n",
                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/d4bd8b8a-f499-40cb-8dd6-2940e9af9494.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>a. Chứng minh \n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c74729c8-e115-4d44-85e2-c1c2ce6c7b61.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/2f4fae62-cc2e-4a5f-8548-6c486546767f.png\"/> ta có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/273698b5-e495-4282-a465-1fe9ee53b31f.png\"/> là góc chung\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/b5b362a3-109f-43d9-a623-9a4998ec2b6f.png\"/>\n (g.g)\n<br>b. Chứng minh <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/63476b17-d5cf-47c5-87d8-bdc7ab7f89f3.png\"/>\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/29bbae92-dfbb-4c54-b3f6-f8f0ad9d8f78.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1863332b-64e0-4ff2-a05b-22a901a82653.png\"/>, ta có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/7b2848c8-1e27-451d-a09e-edd66b112917.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/8b33077e-4f78-43ef-b74a-488d706ce534.png\"/> (do BE là phân giác của góc <i>ABC</i>)\n (g.g)\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/7f1cedaa-e91c-4303-9d56-f01027f04580.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/153759ed-5e4f-4aa5-b75c-6bd97e251e4c.png\"/>\n<br>c. Tính <i>AF\n</i><br>* Theo định lý Pythagore, ta có:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/2d5390f2-6812-42c3-ae55-f36f1e85d166.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a937a83f-195c-4287-83e2-7dedcbe3eb9a.png\"/>\n<br>Chứng minh: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9a65064e-0123-45c0-89bd-2cff55b3c0b1.png\"/> cân tại <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/b5edf6f0-927b-405b-a8c6-23590df751bb.png\"/>\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/9287f2f8-a010-4562-97e1-ec22fe00357e.png\"/> có <i>BE</i> là phân giác của góc <i>ABC\n</i><br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/70081421-1ade-48dc-94e3-08bf14fed4d7.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a0fba358-720e-49b2-bfb0-521d61400924.png\"/>\n<br>Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/6a5719ee-8362-4224-8033-7d605ac7bff4.png\"/>\n",
